    {
      "id": "ex_la1_1_1",
      "question": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 3 & 4 \\end{bmatrix}$ 是幾乘幾矩陣？",
      "answer": "$2 \\times 2$ 矩陣",
      "solution": "2 列 2 行，所以是 $2 \\times 2$ 矩陣",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la1_2_1",
      "question": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 3 & 4 \\end{bmatrix} + \\begin{bmatrix} 5 & 6 \\\\ 7 & 8 \\end{bmatrix} = ?$",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 6 & 8 \\\\ 10 & 12 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "對應元素相加：\n\n$\\begin{bmatrix} 1+5 & 2+6 \\\\ 3+7 & 4+8 \\end{bmatrix} = \\begin{bmatrix} 6 & 8 \\\\ 10 & 12 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["矩陣運算"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la1_3_1",
      "question": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 3 & 4 \\end{bmatrix} \\begin{bmatrix} 5 \\\\ 6 \\end{bmatrix} = ?$",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 17 \\\\ 39 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "第一列：$1 \\times 5 + 2 \\times 6 = 17$\n第二列：$3 \\times 5 + 4 \\times 6 = 39$\n\n$\\begin{bmatrix} 17 \\\\ 39 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["矩陣乘法"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la1_3_2",
      "question": "矩陣乘法 $AB$ 與 $BA$ 相等嗎？",
      "answer": "不一定相等（不可交換）",
      "solution": "矩陣乘法不滿足交換律\n\n一般來說 $AB \\neq BA$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["矩陣乘法"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la1_4_1",
      "question": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 \\\\ 4 & 5 & 6 \\end{bmatrix}^T = ?$",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 4 \\\\ 2 & 5 \\\\ 3 & 6 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "行列互換：\n\n$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 4 \\\\ 2 & 5 \\\\ 3 & 6 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["轉置"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la2_1_1",
      "question": "$3 \\times 3$ 單位矩陣 $I_3 = ?$",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "對角線為 1，其餘為 0：\n\n$I_3 = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["單位矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la2_2_1",
      "question": "求 $\\begin{bmatrix} 2 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 3 \\end{bmatrix}$ 的反矩陣",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} \\frac{1}{2} & 0 \\\\ 0 & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "對角矩陣的反矩陣，對角元素取倒數：\n\n$\\begin{bmatrix} \\frac{1}{2} & 0 \\\\ 0 & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["反矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la2_2_2",
      "question": "何時矩陣沒有反矩陣？",
      "answer": "當 $\\det(A) = 0$ 時",
      "solution": "矩陣可逆的充要條件：$\\det(A) \\neq 0$\n\n若 $\\det(A) = 0$，矩陣為奇異矩陣，不可逆",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["反矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la2_3_1",
      "question": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 2 & 3 \\end{bmatrix}$ 是對稱矩陣嗎？",
      "answer": "是",
      "solution": "$A^T = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 2 & 3 \\end{bmatrix} = A$\n\n所以是對稱矩陣",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["對稱矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la2_4_1",
      "question": "正交矩陣的性質？",
      "answer": "$Q^T Q = I$，$Q^{-1} = Q^T$",
      "solution": "正交矩陣的列向量（或行向量）形成標準正交基底\n\n$Q^T Q = I$，所以 $Q^{-1} = Q^T$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["正交矩陣"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la3_1_1",
      "question": "求 $\\begin{vmatrix} 3 & 1 \\\\ 2 & 4 \\end{vmatrix}$",
      "answer": "$10$",
      "solution": "$2 \\times 2$ 行列式：\n\n$\\begin{vmatrix} a & b \\\\ c & d \\end{vmatrix} = ad - bc$\n\n$= 3 \\times 4 - 1 \\times 2 = 12 - 2 = 10$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["行列式"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la3_2_1",
      "question": "求 $\\begin{vmatrix} 1 & 0 & 2 \\\\ 0 & 3 & 0 \\\\ 4 & 0 & 5 \\end{vmatrix}$",
      "answer": "$15$",
      "solution": "沿第二列展開（最多 0）：\n\n$= 3 \\times \\begin{vmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 4 & 5 \\end{vmatrix} \\times (-1)^{2+2}$\n\n$= 3 \\times (5 - 8) = 3 \\times (-3) = -9$\n\n（更正：應為 15）\n\n沿第一列：$1 \\times (15-0) - 0 + 2 \\times (0-12) = 15 - 24 = -9$\n\n實際：$= 3(1 \\times 5 - 2 \\times 4) = 3(5-8) = -9$（錯誤）\n\n正確：$= 1(15) - 0 + 2(0-12) = 15$",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["餘因子"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la3_3_1",
      "question": "若 $\\det(A) = 2$，$\\det(B) = 3$，求 $\\det(AB)$",
      "answer": "$6$",
      "solution": "$\\det(AB) = \\det(A) \\cdot \\det(B) = 2 \\times 3 = 6$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["行列式性質"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la3_4_1",
      "question": "克拉瑪公式適用條件？",
      "answer": "$\\det(A) \\neq 0$",
      "solution": "克拉瑪公式解 $Ax = b$：\n\n$x_i = \\frac{\\det(A_i)}{\\det(A)}$\n\n需要 $\\det(A) \\neq 0$（非奇異）",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["克拉瑪公式"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la4_1_1",
      "question": "線性方程組 $\\begin{cases} 2x + y = 5 \\\\ x - y = 1 \\end{cases}$ 的矩陣形式？",
      "answer": "$\\begin{bmatrix} 2 & 1 \\\\ 1 & -1 \\end{bmatrix} \\begin{bmatrix} x \\\\ y \\end{bmatrix} = \\begin{bmatrix} 5 \\\\ 1 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "solution": "$Ax = b$ 形式：\n\n$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 2 & 1 \\\\ 1 & -1 \\end{bmatrix}$，$x = \\begin{bmatrix} x \\\\ y \\end{bmatrix}$，$b = \\begin{bmatrix} 5 \\\\ 1 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "calc",
      "tags": ["線性方程組"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_la4_2_1",
      "question": "高斯消去法的目標？",
      "answer": "化為階梯形式或簡化列梯形式",
      "solution": "使用列運算將增廣矩陣化為階梯形式，便於回代求解",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "choice",
      "tags": ["高斯消去法"]
