      "solution": "線性組合：\n\n$= \\begin{bmatrix} 2 \\\\ 0 \\end{bmatrix} + \\begin{bmatrix} 0 \\\\ 3 \\end{bmatrix} = \\begin{bmatrix} 2 \\\\ 3 \\end{bmatrix}$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
